{"tid":778812,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"支那U20女子世界盃補時攞烏龍失波出局","createTime":"2018-08-14T03:19:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-14T04:49:49.000Z","uid":37528,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9dd2a91df4c967ff94483f101afc33b6cc9d6bc1","tid":778812,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T03:19:46.000Z","msg":"中國U20女足周一在法國舉行的U20女子世界盃D組第三輪分組賽戰至補時被尼日利亞以1:1逼和，結果因得失球差不及對手，無緣出線8強。<br />\n<br />\n今場比賽，中國U20女足於41分鐘由張琳艷的入球先開紀錄，惟戰至補時竇加星擺烏龍，尼日利亞以1:1逼和中國，兩隊戰績同是三戰一勝一和一負，但尼日利亞入兩球失兩球，中國則入三球失四球，因得失球差不及對手而屈居小組第三，未能晉級。早已穩奪出線權的德國，於最後一輪賽事以3:2戰勝海地，三戰全勝得9分順利以小組首名出線。<br />\n<br />\n仲要烏龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd613c7f723e9b0a2dd2e8850df74478f5d8f05d","tid":778812,"uid":3194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T04:06:56.000Z","msg":"竇加星?<br />\n乜撚野名黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02b6dbd9f74e05b1f3a97c779af48b003bf57d5e","tid":778812,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd613c7f723e9b0a2dd2e8850df74478f5d8f05d","tid":778812,"uid":3194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T04:06:56.000Z","msg":"竇加星?<br />\n乜撚野名黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T04:18:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5617c9e7884db1e8a98458b4e4e3d8f86c6c69bd","tid":778812,"uid":6366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"02b6dbd9f74e05b1f3a97c779af48b003bf57d5e","tid":778812,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd613c7f723e9b0a2dd2e8850df74478f5d8f05d","tid":778812,"uid":3194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T04:06:56.000Z","msg":"竇加星?<br />\n乜撚野名黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T04:18